com.parkingtycoon.helpers

Class Delegate<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.parkingtycoon.helpers.Delegate<T>

  • public class Delegate<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Tread safe implementation of C# delegates. This class is a Helper to the Observer pattern - The old scenario would contain a ArrayList per Observable + the required functions
    Author:
    GGG

      • process

        public void process(Delegate.Starter<T> starter)
        If you want multithreading support than you are required to call process to process the data between the queues so that there can not accrue a multithreading problem.
        Parameters:
        starter - the Lambda or method reference that will point to the function that we will call only once on the first time that a item moves between the waiting queues and the list.
